At a high level it [follows this flow diagram](https://coggle.it/diagram/V0hkiP976OIbGpy8/t/vanilla-pattern).

### Who

- VF core maintainers
- EMBL Communications' Digital and Design teams
- EMBL-EBI Web Development, UX and Communications teams
- Nominated service representatives
  - Relationship with EMBL-EBI Web Guidelines Committee
- The requestor(s) of a new component or change

### When

In addition to the quarterly consultation, we meet on regular basis in three channels:

- Design consultation, every other Monday
- UX consultation, every other Tuesday
- Technical consultation, monthly on the first Thursday

These form initial discussion and debate on new ideas before they are further tested and actioned on the GitHub issue queue.

