### What if my idea gets rejected?

The agreed implementation doesn't cover my needs?

Even if your need can't be accommodated:

- the Visual Framework accommodate customisation at the edge (in Sass or JavaScript) or core changes (by bringing your own build process or design tokens)
- you can [create and use a custom component in your local project]({{ '/building' | url }}) and share the component on npm for others to use

The Visual Framework allows "local rule". You won't be blocked from adding and overriding components.

